{"name": "Speculations #1 1", "description": "Speculations is a unique perspective on the development phase of the fully onchain project, Mempools by troels_a.

Mempools explores the convergence of human memory and blockchain processes, through generative artworks. Speculations offers a curated selection of renders from this process and insights into the creative method behind its hereditary project.

Mempools pieces go through development phase called epochs that span multiple years. With Speculations the process have been sped up to generate pieces as might look devades into the future, had they been generated by the Mempools contract.
